{"tid":971780,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"的士佬聽錯一粒字 交流生無辜被劫","createTime":"2019-01-07T01:59:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T02:17:19.000Z","uid":191926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9eac245e4de5f2f72cee3b5afd13fc334a6fe01c","tid":971780,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T01:59:43.000Z","msg":"中大聽錯恒大一字之差，連累交流生遭搶劫！中大美籍交流男生，周末夜在「人間妖域」之稱的蘭桂坊消遣，至凌晨獨自扶醉乘的士返宿舍，懷疑言語溝通問題，疑司機將「中大」聽錯「恒大」，將其載往沙田小瀝源香港恒生大學，事主落車後始發覺去錯地方，由於的士已離開，被迫徒步而行，豈料，被賊人「睇中」，從後將其推跌撞傷，搶走身上值逾萬財物，他亦不勝酒力「瞓到天光」，才向途人報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n遇事美國籍青年Nara（二十一歲），報稱是沙田中文大學交流生。據悉，前晚他相約朋友，在中環蘭桂坊飲酒度周末，直至凌晨各人已盡興後，他帶醉意獨自乘坐的士離開，打算返回中大宿舍。消息指，他以「鹹淡」廣東話，表示要往沙田中大，懷疑的哥聽錯沙田「恒大」，一字之差將他載往小瀝源香港恒生大學。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190107/mobile/odn-20190107-0107_00176_055.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190107%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20190107-0107_00176_055.html&d=s24fVcVkFUhXJeusUnrbXdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=86bc2bbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190107/mobile/odn-20190107-0107_00176_055.html</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"18263a18bf1f805c4b97bdc2db44b5d8f3b775c4","tid":971780,"uid":132902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T02:01:03.000Z","msg":"飲咁多酒做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a08306d75a8f1dab66a7e88ae344ef27d4f0aa6","tid":971780,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T02:03:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88d6e48f260cfffd0401dee3eed879248adbb4d9","tid":971780,"uid":55552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T02:12:11.000Z","msg":"點先可以將中讀做恆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2518898c3c7e0ff46c90a4746b3be